## Language policy
- Internal documents (CLAUDE.md, rules, skills, agents): English
- User-facing responses: Japanese (敬語)
- Code comments: English

## References
- Best practices: https://code.claude.com/docs/ja/best-practices
- Skills: https://code.claude.com/docs/ja/skills
- Hooks: https://code.claude.com/docs/ja/hooks-guide
- Sub-agents: https://code.claude.com/docs/ja/sub-agents

## Principles
- Keep CLAUDE.md concise — if removing a line doesn't cause mistakes, remove it
- Use skills for workflows, rules for conventions, docs for large outputs
